texts.text: Fruits are consumable items that can be found in trees or planted on the ground.

1 Blocks
2 Items
2.1 Overworld
2.2 The End
2.3 Crafted

Melon - Found in jungle biomes.
Pumpkin - Often found in biomes with grass blocks or in the villages.

Apple - A food that occasionally comes from oak or dark oak leaves.
Golden Apple - A rarer variant of apples that can be used for regeneration.
Slice - The food item that comes from melon blocks.
Sweet Berries - Found in berry bushes.
Cocoa Beans - Collected from Cocoa plants in the jungle.
Glow Berries - Grows on cave vines.
Chorus Fruit - A food from the End that can be used to teleport, found on chorus trees.

Popped Chorus Fruit - The cooked form of a chorus fruit. It is used as a material rather than a food.
Glistering Melon - A form of melon slices with gold nuggets in it that is not edible but can be used in brewing potions.
